%N A397236 Expansion of 1/(1 - x^3 - x^4 - 2*x^5 - x^7).
%C A397236 Number of compositions of n into parts 3, 4, 5, and 7 where there are two sorts of part 5.
%H A397236 <a href="/index/Rec#order_07">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (0,0,1,1,2,0,1).
%F A397236 a(n) = a(n-3) + a(n-4) + 2*a(n-5) + a(n-7).
%F A397236 G.f.: 1/( (1+x^2) * (1-x^2-x^3-x^5) ).
%o A397236 (PARI) my(N=50, x='x+O('x^N)); Vec(1/(1-x^3-x^4-2*x^5-x^7))
